## Part 2: Outreach Status Definitions

| Status | Definition | Trigger |
|---|---|---|
| **Cold** | Contact created. Touch 1 task assigned. Connection request not yet sent. | Flow 1 fires on contact creation. |
| **Attempting Contact** | Actively working through the sequence. | Touch 2 executes (first auto-send email). |
| **Engaged** | Meaningful positive reply received. | `Meaningful_Reply__c` = true AND `Reply_Type__c` = Positive. |
| **Meeting Scheduled** | Discovery call or meeting booked. | Dylan manually updates. Creates Opportunity at Qualify stage. |
| **Deferred** | Sequence complete with no engagement, or "not interested" reply. Terminal state — no re-entry. | Touch 13 completes, or `Reply_Type__c` = Not Interested / Bad Timing. |

### Permanent Exclusion
`Exclude_From_Sequence__c` = true → excluded from ALL current and future sequences. Triggered by Hard Opt-Out, manual exclusion, or legacy tagging. Separate from Deferred.

