- Casual, conversational, human tone. No corporate speak.
- 3-4 sentences max for early emails and LinkedIn messages.
- Goal: get a meaningful reply. Not book a meeting, not pitch.
- All copy is AI-generated but personalized — job title, LinkedIn activity, company news, Apollo signals.
- Every task includes drafted copy. No task requires writing from scratch.
