### Flow 5: Email Open Counter — DEFERRED TO V2

For v1, Dylan manually updates `Email_Opens_Count__c` when he notices opens on the Activity Timeline. This avoids the complexity of building a reliable EmailMessage trigger or scheduled counter during the initial deployment.

Future v2 implementation: scheduled Flow running every 2 hours querying EmailMessage records with Status = "Read" and incrementing the counter with dedup prevention.

